Hey Whats Up? Nothing Much here. Well tonight is the first Varsity football game away in Berkley. Im excited its going to be fun. Thats all i pretty much have to do. I havent done much lately besides sit around and play Snood lol i deciced to take this last week slow before i have to go back to school for the year but im excited about school starting. It's going to be fun and i hope it goes by fast again this year. But anyways im going to go i have to start getting ready.
Im out
Kelly

Hello, I did'nt write last night because well i was just to damn tired. I didn't go to bed the other night tell like 4am so i went tot bed early last night.Anyways yesterday i had to work and went out to breakfast with Rob La Forest so it was pretty cool. Today i had cheerleading and well i don't have to work today Thank God and so i'll just be chilling. (With my friends that is) So anyways im going to go . got lots to do!

Hello! How are you? Im good, Well today was just another crappy day in the life of Kelly. I had to work again of course but Sundays are alright because there not very busy at all. Then me, Mike, and Matt hung out for a bit tell Mike had to go in because hes a Loser right now with a 11 o clock curfew(lol Im kidding)If your wondering everythings cool with me and him and well after that me and Matt played a trick on Heymes again lol Like always but it was fun!But anyways im going to go and talk to my best friend in the whole world Rob Laforest lol !

Hey There Whats Up? Well today was an alright day. Lets see i did'nt do much besides i had to work again and i didn't get off tell like 10 so i hung out with Paul G,Lauren M,Mike J,and Ryan Ash. We didn't do much besides sit outside and watch the storm which was pretty neat. But i called mike and got some things settled with him it's just so hard because he got mad at me for everything and i can't help the feelings i have inside of me i mean i do like him but hey what can you do.

Hey Everyone, Well today was a an alright day i guess. I had to work of and then i went to the movies with Steve M because well hes leaving for college and i won't get to see him all year. We saw American Outlaws it was pretty good. But anyways schools starting soon and Im kinda excited at least Im not a Freshman anymore. My life is kinda in the dumps me and mike are no longer friends because i told him how i really felt i mean i was just telling him the truth.
